NAME="instance"
SECTION="group"
SUMMARY="Persistent instance command group"
USAGE="singularity [...] instance.<command> [...]"

print_help() {
cat<<EOF

This is a command group that supports the management of various instance
functions.

IMAGE GROUP COMMANDS:

    instance.list     Print all running container instances
    instance.start    Start a persistent container instance
    instance.stop     Stop and kill all processes within a running instance

All group commands have their own help output:

    $ singularity help instance.start
    $ singularity instance.start --help

For additional help, please visit our public documentation pages which are
found at:

    http://singularity.lbl.gov/
EOF
}
